Comment: 0,0:23:34.98,0:23:35.02,Dialogue,chptr,0,0,0,,{Data viitoare}
Dialogue: 100,0:00:16.58,0:00:18.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hei, mă auzi?!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:18.70,0:00:20.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu-ți da duhul pe aici!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:20.54,0:00:23.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dacă devine prea greu, \Ndoar du-te unde vezi cu ochii!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:24.50,0:00:27.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Trăiește-ți viața așa cum dorești!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:29.50,0:00:30.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Așa voi face.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:15.35,0:01:19.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nu am crezut niciodată \Ncă mă voi întoarce aici.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:36.82,0:01:37.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Intră.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:48.03,0:01:49.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Uite-i...
Dialogue: 100,0:01:51.50,0:01:53.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Regina Demon, Echidna,
Dialogue: 100,0:01:54.01,0:01:55.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}și cei Patru Mari Generali!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:07.73,0:02:10.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}E în regulă. Nu și-au dat seama cine sunt.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:12.04,0:02:14.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nu încă. Trebuie să mă apropii mai mult...
Dialogue: 100,0:02:15.36,0:02:16.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Closer, now...
Dialogue: 100,0:02:39.59,0:02:41.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'Tis I, former Hero Leo Demonhart!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:42.47,0:02:45.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm here to apply for a position in the Demon Army!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:46.39,0:02:48.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not only am I a skilled swordsman
Dialogue: 100,0:02:48.35,0:02:50.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I have also mastered all schools of magic!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:50.67,0:02:53.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I even defeated the Demon Queen Echidna herself in single combat!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:53.44,0:02:55.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am ready and raring to fight for your cause!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:55.98,0:02:58.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I'm well aware of your army's current situation:
Dialogue: 100,0:02:58.57,0:03:02.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your severe understaffing has made recovery nigh-impossible!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:02.81,0:03:06.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do I know this? Because I was the one who decimated your army!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:07.12,0:03:11.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But let's forget the past and look towards the future!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:11.72,0:03:14.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The time has come for a brighter future.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:14.29,0:03:16.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Together, we shall bring ruin to those foolish humans...
Dialogue: 100,0:03:16.82,0:03:18.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and create a glorious Demon Kingdom to last a millennia!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:18.88,0:03:22.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is why I want to be hired to join your army!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:39.36,0:03:42.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was perfect. I got this in the bag.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:42.91,0:03:46.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you stupid?! Why the hell would we hire you?!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:51.13,0:03:53.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you hire me, you'll have an incredibly powerful asset—
Dialogue: 100,0:03:56.70,0:03:58.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll make you the greatest Demon Queen there ever was!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:58.88,0:04:00.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you still talking?!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:01.53,0:04:03.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll help you rapidly grow your workfo—
Dialogue: 100,0:04:03.86,0:04:04.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:05.97,0:04:07.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Under my management, performance will skyrocket, and—
Dialogue: 100,0:04:07.76,0:04:08.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:08.68,0:04:10.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll bring you tea, do all your photocopies!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:10.56,0:04:11.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll clean the bathroom!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:12.52,0:04:14.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And if you hire me in the next twenty minutes...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:14.24,0:04:15.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you'll receive a brand-new... {ED: A BRAND NEW CAR?!}
Dialogue: 100,0:04:15.49,0:04:18.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd like to take a minute to explain a bit more about myself.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:18.80,0:04:22.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One year ago, the Demon Army, under the leadership of Echidna,
Dialogue: 100,0:04:22.99,0:04:26.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,descended upon the human world in a surprise invasion.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:26.91,0:04:30.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His Majesty the King gave me a mission to destroy the Demon Army.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:30.62,0:04:34.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As such, I gathered a party of elite heroes and set out from the capital at once.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:35.33,0:04:38.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was just one problem.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:38.42,0:04:40.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't mean to brag, but I'm really powerful.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:40.06,0:04:46.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As a Royal Knight, I've mastered every weapon and magic known to man.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:46.06,0:04:49.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And to be totally honest, my party members just got in my way.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:49.81,0:04:52.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had a priestess who refused to learn anything that wasn't a healing spell,
Dialogue: 100,0:04:52.85,0:04:55.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a meathead soldier who didn't know jack about magic,
Dialogue: 100,0:04:55.92,0:04:58.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and an archer who was straight-up useless in close range.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:58.52,0:05:01.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still, I forged trusting bonds with those dead weights,
Dialogue: 100,0:05:01.28,0:05:04.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,defeated our enemies with the power of teamwork and friendship,
Dialogue: 100,0:05:04.49,0:05:07.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and watched them fight about room assignments at every inn we stopped at.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:07.74,0:05:09.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was so stupid!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:09.21,0:05:12.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I could've saved the world five times over!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:13.87,0:05:20.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So in the end, I set off by myself, defeated Queen Echidna by myself, and decimated the Demon Army by myself!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:20.29,0:05:21.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's how freakin' strong I am!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:21.91,0:05:24.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's literally no reason not to hire me!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:24.83,0:05:29.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you weren't given a chance because of your demeanor, Master Leo.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:29.14,0:05:31.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I've turned over a new leaf!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:31.45,0:05:34.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah! He's a totally new leaf!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:34.75,0:05:37.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Quiet down, Lily. Stop jumping.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:37.30,0:05:39.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's literally no reason not to hire him!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:41.19,0:05:46.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, let her be, Mernes. Lily's just happy to see him again.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:50.27,0:05:52.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know it's late to be realizing this,
Dialogue: 100,0:05:52.33,0:05:55.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but you've got a real diverse group here.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:57.69,0:06:00.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just tell us what you want already and make it quick.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:00.46,0:06:04.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If Queen Echidna found out we were meeting with you, she'd burn the castle to the ground.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:05.01,0:06:08.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we're only meeting with you because you wouldn't stop pestering us,
Dialogue: 100,0:06:08.13,0:06:11.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,even after you were thrown out!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:13.77,0:06:18.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right. Let me start with a little presentation, then.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:18.59,0:06:19.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A present...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:19.77,0:06:24.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd like to remind each of you just how powerful I am.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:24.97,0:06:26.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And why would you do that?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:26.83,0:06:30.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll admit that my demeanor can be problematic at times.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:30.34,0:06:33.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even so, the fact that I was strong enough to defeat all four of you solo
Dialogue: 100,0:06:33.17,0:06:36.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,should be enough to qualify me for the position.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:36.47,0:06:39.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By reminding each of you how you were defeated,
Dialogue: 100,0:06:39.05,0:06:40.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hope to gain your endorsement.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:40.78,0:06:41.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:44.02,0:06:47.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see! I can most certainly vouch for your skill.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:47.93,0:06:52.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'd been far too long since someone bested me in a fair duel!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:52.55,0:06:54.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not a laughing matter!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:54.51,0:06:59.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come, now, it's wonderful to cross swords with such a powerful opponent!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:59.71,0:07:01.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you agree, Master Leo?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:02.21,0:07:05.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The first of the Four Generals I fought was this one,
Dialogue: 100,0:07:06.28,0:07:11.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Edvard the Dragon General, a.k.a. "The Red Roar."
Dialogue: 100,0:07:19.27,0:07:23.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In terms of raw stats, he was the toughest one of the bunch.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:24.84,0:07:29.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dragonfolk and their draconic scales are ridiculously tough.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:30.92,0:07:34.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I had to fight him just with my sword, who knows how that could have gone.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:36.85,0:07:40.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Luckily for me, he's the kind of idiot—
Dialogue: 100,0:07:41.04,0:07:45.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Er, noble warrior who charges in solo, so the fight was way easier. {ED: LEEROY JENKINS!}
Dialogue: 100,0:07:45.61,0:07:46.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Great stuff!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:47.28,0:07:50.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've a question for you, actually. Why do you serve Echidna, anyway?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:51.25,0:07:54.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're strong enough to go for world domination. {ED: A self-reminder to watch Love After World Domination after this.}
Dialogue: 100,0:07:55.41,0:07:57.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why, you ask?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:59.73,0:08:02.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I've never given it proper thought.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:03.39,0:08:09.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I guess it's 'cause I want to live the life of a proper swordsman, dueling strong opponents.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:09.76,0:08:10.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 100,0:08:10.83,0:08:13.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rulin' the world is busy work.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:13.51,0:08:17.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't get to spend as much time with my daughter Julietta.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:17.51,0:08:19.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't bear it, no sir!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:22.07,0:08:24.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't know you have a daughter...
Dialogue: 100,0:08:24.28,0:08:27.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I actually feel quite bad for you.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:27.54,0:08:29.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? Why?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:29.48,0:08:34.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you came here alone, then you must not have any friends to spend your time with.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:34.95,0:08:38.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're one to talk, Mernes.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:38.57,0:08:41.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm 100% sure you don't have any friends, either.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:42.11,0:08:45.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After I defeated Edvard, I fought this guy here:
Dialogue: 100,0:08:45.65,0:08:49.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mernes the Shadowless General, a.k.a. "The Unseen Blade." {ED: Maidenless?}
Dialogue: 100,0:08:49.88,0:08:55.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rumors say he's a deadly young half-demon who was once with the Assassin's Guild.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:56.22,0:08:59.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, when I fought him, his speed and strength were unmatched.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:00.37,0:09:03.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He might have beaten me if he had five more minutes.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:03.05,0:09:06.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately for him, I didn't plan on contesting his speed.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:08.66,0:09:14.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I casted Crimson Comet, an AoE{Area of Effect} spell, to blow him away,
Dialogue: 100,0:09:14.33,0:09:18.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but it ended up destroying everything in its radius, which included the church.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:18.12,0:09:21.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And honestly, I had a rougher time after I'd defeated him.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:21.83,0:09:27.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Apparently the blast was so big, it took out one of the town's historical sites.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:28.21,0:09:32.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened after that fight with the townspeople?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:32.79,0:09:34.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you ever pay them ba—
Dialogue: 100,0:09:34.01,0:09:38.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello hello? I can't hear you! You'll have to speak up!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:38.39,0:09:42.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't hear ya! You'll have to speak up!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:42.96,0:09:44.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Lily, but...
Dialogue: 100,0:09:44.37,0:09:47.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Leo! Did I sound like you? Did I?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:50.66,0:09:54.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After Mernes came this little surprise.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:54.58,0:09:57.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lily the Beast General, a.k.a. "The Ruthless Fang."
Dialogue: 100,0:09:57.74,0:10:00.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our first encounter was completely ridiculous.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:00.24,0:10:03.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I took shelter from the rain under a tree,
Dialogue: 100,0:10:03.05,0:10:06.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and when I looked to the side, she was there, standing next to me.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:06.72,0:10:12.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the time, she had amnesia, no family, no friends, and nowhere to go.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:13.16,0:10:17.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wasn't about to leave a little kid out there alone, so I took care of her for a few days.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:18.84,0:10:24.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But then she remembered who she was, and she introduced herself as the Beast General Lily. Great.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:26.97,0:10:31.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had to fight her eventually, so I fought her. Of course, I won.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:32.38,0:10:34.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pretty, uh, easily...
Dialogue: 100,0:10:34.61,0:10:40.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Later, I learned that in their tribe, if someone strong defeats you in combat,
Dialogue: 100,0:10:40.16,0:10:42.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they're the person you're destined to be with.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:43.92,0:10:46.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why'd this have to happen to me?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:47.73,0:10:52.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Leo! When're you gonna marry me? C'mon, marry me!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:52.50,0:10:56.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe when you're just a little older{, sweetie}.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:56.32,0:11:03.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna wait! I wanna marry you now! Right now!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:03.18,0:11:08.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And finally, I fought Shutina the Sorcerer General, a.k.a. "The Almighty Mage."
Dialogue: 100,0:11:08.60,0:11:12.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,People say that she had a far greater pool of mana than other succubi,
Dialogue: 100,0:11:12.27,0:11:16.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and had mastered all types of sorcery, including ancient and accursed.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:17.22,0:11:23.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Knowing that, I started our battle with the AoE spell Stasis, which prevents spellcasting altogether,
Dialogue: 100,0:11:23.81,0:11:26.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and challenged her in physical combat.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:30.29,0:11:33.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was... embarrassingly weak.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:35.80,0:11:40.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After two minutes, you started crying for mercy. It's kinda sad, really.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:40.30,0:11:45.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm a mage! Of course I'm no match in hand-to-hand combat!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:45.99,0:11:48.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure, but a real professional would have a plan B.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:48.53,0:11:52.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to have a plan B for someone who can nullify all my spells?!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:52.81,0:11:57.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There literally isn't anyone in the world who can do that the second they walk up!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:57.78,0:11:59.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Except there is: me.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:01.03,0:12:03.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forget that! What is all this about, anyway?!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:03.91,0:12:06.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you I was gonna give you a presentation.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:07.12,0:12:10.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I admit, I did want to hear how he defeated the rest of you.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:10.40,0:12:12.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It all happened so fast.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:12.50,0:12:14.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Agreed!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:14.00,0:12:16.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was curious, too!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:16.01,0:12:19.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you were by far the most useless of all of us, Shutina.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:20.59,0:12:22.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Agreed!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:22.05,0:12:23.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Poor Shutina!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:26.97,0:12:29.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will you just get to the point already?!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:31.14,0:12:35.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you, a hero, come to interview for a job with the Demon Army?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:35.62,0:12:37.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what I want to know!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:38.65,0:12:42.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do you even want to join the Demon Army?!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:48.32,0:12:50.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't come here to mess with you.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:51.86,0:12:52.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll answer your question.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:53.45,0:12:56.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you why I left my life of fighting the Demon Army behind,
Dialogue: 100,0:12:56.48,0:13:00.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and why I decided to defect to your side after so long.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:01.28,0:13:02.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So listen up.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:00.48,0:14:07.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After defeating the four of you and Echnida herself, I returned to Renailles.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:13.87,0:14:21.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there was no celebration or cheering to be heard.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:22.30,0:14:29.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Instead, I was met with long stares and sharp glares filled with shock, fear, and skepticism.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:28.73,0:14:29.44,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Is he really human?!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:29.44,0:14:31.22,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,No, he's a monster in human clothing!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:32.24,0:14:33.43,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:34.40,0:14:38.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fear and worry spread like wildfire. I couldn't stop it.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:43.13,0:14:46.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Word spread via letter, messenger pigeon, magic, and posters:
Dialogue: 100,0:14:46.55,0:14:50.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The Hero Leo is a danger to us all."
Dialogue: 100,0:14:50.20,0:14:54.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We cannot allow that man to wander free through our streets!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:54.12,0:15:00.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We cannot let him wreck havoc upon us. We must put an end to that man— No, that monster!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:00.25,0:15:02.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's right! Kill him!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:04.53,0:15:09.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was the new evil to be killed. That was what humanity came to believe.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:11.62,0:15:16.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the following days, I was accosted by assassins.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:16.81,0:15:21.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't believe their stupidity! I took out the Demon Queen all by myself!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:21.81,0:15:25.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did they really think I'd let some half-rate assassins do me in?!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:26.18,0:15:29.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some time after that, I was called to the palace to speak with the King.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:29.90,0:15:36.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was your actions that kept the Philosopher's Stone safe, and for that, I thank you.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:36.12,0:15:38.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It pains me to make this decree,
Dialogue: 100,0:15:39.06,0:15:43.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but as the kingdom's protector, I cannot turn a blind eye to the concerns of my people.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:44.09,0:15:46.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Great Hero Leo,
Dialogue: 100,0:15:46.05,0:15:50.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hereby sentence you to exile.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:58.49,0:15:59.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:00.81,0:16:02.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Never forget, though,
Dialogue: 100,0:16:03.94,0:16:06.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that I have the utmost trust in your goodwill.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:14.25,0:16:19.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did I risk my life to protect this rotten world?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:19.97,0:16:23.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did I fight tooth and nail against the Demon Army?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:24.53,0:16:27.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everything was suddenly so meaningless.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:27.14,0:16:31.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never had a home, so I had nowhere to go.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:31.37,0:16:34.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All I could do was wander aimlessly from village to village.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:37.83,0:16:39.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, one day...
Dialogue: 100,0:16:39.14,0:16:41.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you hear what the Demon Army's doing?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:41.83,0:16:45.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they're recruiting, right? Can you believe it?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:45.61,0:16:50.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're actually trying to do it again, after getting their asses handed to them by that hero.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:50.74,0:16:52.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'd think they learned their lesson.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:52.10,0:16:54.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That Demon Queen Echidna isn't the sharpest tool in the shed, is she?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:54.92,0:16:55.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Echidna...
Dialogue: 100,0:16:55.99,0:17:00.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure isn't. Only a matter of time before we stop hearin' about her.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:00.71,0:17:01.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:01.97,0:17:03.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Echidna, huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:05.69,0:17:06.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened to that thing'a yours?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:06.96,0:17:09.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know why...
Dialogue: 100,0:17:09.40,0:17:13.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I concluded that the only place willing to take me in
Dialogue: 100,0:17:13.19,0:17:17.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was the Demon Army itself.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:19.25,0:17:22.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I stayed up all night working on my spiel,
Dialogue: 100,0:17:22.76,0:17:24.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,putting together a fancy presentation,
Dialogue: 100,0:17:24.39,0:17:26.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I crossed the endless sands,
Dialogue: 100,0:17:26.75,0:17:29.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,scaled the treacherous mountains,
Dialogue: 100,0:17:29.07,0:17:30.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,all to arrive here.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:31.54,0:17:37.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the world is hellbent on killing me, then I just have to kill them first.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:40.49,0:17:43.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that's why I want to work for you.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:55.69,0:17:58.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Very well, Leo the Hero.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:58.25,0:18:02.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You poor, pitiful soul, who devoted his heart and body to the wrong people.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:03.35,0:18:06.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I sense no falsehoods nor trickery behind your reasons to join with us.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:06.14,0:18:07.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believe you are genuine.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:08.17,0:18:11.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Sorcerer General Shutina.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:16.72,0:18:19.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've definitely gotten over a big hurdle here.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:19.43,0:18:20.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 100,0:18:20.70,0:18:23.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You will be subjected to a one-month trial period!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:23.88,0:18:28.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be your manager for that period, and will evaluate your worthiness!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:28.13,0:18:31.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I expect you to produce results during your trial period.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:31.79,0:18:33.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And if those results are unsatisfactory?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:34.09,0:18:35.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then we'll throw you out!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:36.06,0:18:40.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll work hard. I'm pretty done with roughing it out there.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:40.43,0:18:44.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you must not let Queen Echidna know we've hired you at all.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:45.15,0:18:50.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Use a magic item or spell to keep yourself disguised at all times.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:50.64,0:18:53.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You got it. So, are there any issues you've been dealing with as of late?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:53.65,0:18:58.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our top priorities are bolstering our ranks, repairing the castle, and procuring weapons.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:58.20,0:19:02.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, there's budgeting, improving employee benefits, and providing counseling...
Dialogue: 100,0:19:02.24,0:19:05.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We also need to perform maintenance on the mana reactors, train any new recruits...
Dialogue: 100,0:19:07.16,0:19:10.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rebuilding an army is a lot of work!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:10.00,0:19:11.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And not just for Shutina!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:11.81,0:19:14.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've got a lotta work to do, too, y'know!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:14.84,0:19:16.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop jumping, Lily.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:16.69,0:19:19.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been helping with loj... lojistics?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:19.40,0:19:24.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like, getting supplies and stuff, and it's been really hard!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:24.39,0:19:26.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's so much I gotta do!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:26.87,0:19:28.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:30.19,0:19:32.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know logistics is...
Dialogue: 100,0:19:32.90,0:19:35.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the most important part of any...
Dialogue: 100,0:19:35.32,0:19:39.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right! It's the most important, and they asked me to do it!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:39.03,0:19:41.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that amazing? It's amazing!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:41.27,0:19:44.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, it's even worse than I thought.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:44.48,0:19:46.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Watch it!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:46.45,0:19:48.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is all your fault!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:48.17,0:19:50.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Calm down there, Shutina.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:50.42,0:19:55.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've gotta admit, it'd be a relief to have Master Leo on our side.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:55.68,0:19:57.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I suppose, but still...
Dialogue: 100,0:19:58.42,0:19:59.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:00.85,0:20:05.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Very well. I can be calm. I'm calm, yes...
Dialogue: 100,0:20:05.83,0:20:12.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's let bygones be bygones! Glad to have ya, Master Leo!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:12.46,0:20:13.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Glad to have ya!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:13.78,0:20:17.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Same here. Thanks, Edvard. You too, Lily.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:19.03,0:20:22.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mernes. You good? I'm looking forward to working with you, too.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:25.76,0:20:26.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Leo the Hero.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:27.29,0:20:29.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you can produce good results during this trial period,
Dialogue: 100,0:20:29.72,0:20:32.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,we will not cheapen your efforts by bringing you in as an 'unpaid intern.'
Dialogue: 100,0:20:32.63,0:20:37.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We, the Four Great Generals, will recommend to Queen Echidna that you be officially taken in.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:40.77,0:20:43.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't let you down, I promise.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:47.06,0:20:52.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're in dire need of people, especially those skilled in management.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:52.53,0:20:56.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then those bolstered ranks need training. There's a lot of tasks on the table.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:56.15,0:20:59.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're essentially rebuilding from zero.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:59.23,0:21:03.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're not just struggling; they're on the brink of closing up shop.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:03.68,0:21:07.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that's exactly why I need to talk to Echidna,
Dialogue: 100,0:21:07.49,0:21:10.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and ask her the question I've been pondering since that day.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:13.05,0:21:14.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:14.88,0:21:16.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Q-Queen Echidna!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:16.13,0:21:17.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You heard my orders!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:17.67,0:21:20.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While this is an invasion, we must not kill whenever possible!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:20.71,0:21:24.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Any territory we occupy must be ruled peacefully!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:25.08,0:21:27.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She forbids indiscriminate killing.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:28.43,0:21:32.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What cause is so important that she would handicap her army like that?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:33.55,0:21:38.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why does she still refuse to leave the human world despite her utter defeat?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:42.19,0:21:44.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I need to ask her these questions and more.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:44.78,0:21:47.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Live your life the way you want!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:49.58,0:21:54.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just you watch, Echidna. I'll be a part of your army before you know it.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:59.44,0:22:03.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the story of how I did just that.
